# core2ai Consumer Impact (db2ai)

`@core2ai/core` is installed via **GitHub pin** (`github:annettedorothea/core2ai#vX.Y.Z`), not a sibling `file:` path.

## After `npm run core2ai:refresh-pin` or a new core2ai tag

From the **db2ai workspace root**:

1. `npm run bundle:mcp-runtime` — rebuilds [`packages/cli/resources/mcp-serve-emitted.mjs`](../../packages/cli/resources/mcp-serve-emitted.mjs)
2. `npm run generate:all` — copies MCP host to `packages/extension/demos/generated/cli/mcp-serve.mjs`
3. `npm run langium:generate && npm run build && npm run check`
4. **Restart MCP servers** in Cursor

Editing `../core2ai` alone does **not** update bundled `mcp-serve.mjs` or `node_modules/@core2ai/core`.

## Release workflow

Use skill **core2ai release** (canonical: `core2ai/.cursor/skills/core2ai-release/`).

See also [github-core-dependency.mdc](./github-core-dependency.mdc), [codegen-generated-quality.mdc](./codegen-generated-quality.mdc), and [generated-output-do-not-edit.mdc](./generated-output-do-not-edit.mdc).
